#: ../../reference/datamodel.rst:3987
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The :meth:`~object.__hash__`, :meth:`~object.__iter__`, "
":meth:`~object.__reversed__`, :meth:`~object.__contains__`, "
":meth:`~object.__class_getitem__` and :meth:`~os.PathLike.__fspath__` "
